title: Hotel relais Madeleine
description:
The Relais Madeleine is an intimate hotel in the 9th arrondissement of Paris, two steps away from the Madeleine Church. Although it is located in a buzzing area of Paris, the hotel offers pleasant spacious and quiet rooms. The reception is warm, the decoration is refined and the rooms are comfortable.
Step out of the hotel and meet with a sea of possibilities. A little culture? The hotel is located near the greatest museums such as the Pinacothèque, the Musée d'Orsay, the Louvre and the Opera, as well as many theaters such as the Edouard III and the famous Olympia. For a shopping trip, the rue du Faubourg Saint-Honoré, the place de la Madeleine and their luxury boutiques are a just stone's throw away, not to mention the famous Galeries Lafayette of boulevard Haussmann. Sweet-tooths and gourmets on the other hand will be delighted by Kaspia or the House of Chocolate right right down the street!
http://hotel-relais-madeleine.com/hotel-charme-paris/
